LinuxRemoteFileCopy
-------------------
1. Get Source & Destination Copy Details
2. Check Source & Destination Connectivity
3. Check Ineligible Paths and File Permissions
4. Copy File from Source FilePath to /tmp
5. SCP File from Source /tmp to Destination /tmp
6. Delete from Source /tmp
7. Move File from Destination /tmp to Destination FilePath
8. Change Permissions and Ownership in Destination
9. Verify if Files are actually Copied